title: Billy Martin’s Tavern, Rep. Chip Roy, R-TX

description:
Guests: Congressman Chip Roy, a Texas Republican representing the 21st district, Billy Martin III, owner of Billy Martin’s Tavern, Brian Darling, former Senior Communications Director for Sen. Rand Paul and Founder of Liberty Government Affairs, and Max Burns, Democratic Strategist; Contributor at The Daily Beast and The Independent.
